description.lang: RF9536 - 1000W Incandescent Smart Dimmer ASPIRE RF Dimmers replace regular switches or dimmers to provide local and remote ON/OFF/DIM/BRIGHT control and are compatible with incandescent lighting loads. ASPIRE RF Dimmers provide other programmable functions (scenes, events, association, child lockout, etc.) when used with ASPIRE RF or other Z-Wave compliant controllers*.(*Note: some specific ASPIRE RF features may not be programmable)
